{{Quote|What mountains are those?''"<br />"''The Mountains of the Exalted. The Altar of Promises where the faithful gather each night to be Exulted lies before them.|[[Han Solo/Legends|Han Solo]] and [[Veratil]]|<ref name="TPS">''[[The Paradise Snare]]''</ref>}}
The '''Mountains of the Exalted''' was a small [[Mountain/Legends|mountain]] range located on the [[Hutt/Legends|Hutt]]-controlled jungle [[Planet/Legends|world]] of [[Ylesia/Legends|Ylesia]], near [[Peace City|Colony One]]. The [[Altar of Promises]], used by the [[Priest/Legends|priests]] of the [[Cult of The One and The All]], was located at its base.

